PrecisAuthorization for the leasing by the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to the KANATA RESEARCH PARK CORPORATION, for a term of 49 years, of some 17.7 hectares of land situated at the southeast corner of Herzberg Road at Sandhill Road, in the City of Kanata, Ontario, for the development of a public golf course facility.
